---
import Container from '../common/Container.astro'
---

<section
  class="relative overflow-hidden pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-16 md:pb-24 section-gradient"
  id="hero"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-48 md:w-96 h-48 md:h-96 rounded-full opacity-20" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent) 0%, transparent 70%); animation: pulse-glow 4s ease-in-out infinite;"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-32 -left-32 w-40 md:w-80 h-40 md:h-80 rounded-full opacity-15" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent) 0%, transparent 70%); animation: pulse-glow 5s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: -2s;"></div>
    <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/3 left-1/4 w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background-color: var(--accent); opacity: 0.3; box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent);"></div>
    <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 right-1/3 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full" style="background-color: var(--accent); opacity: 0.2; box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--accent);"></div>
    <svg class="hidden md:block absolute top-0 right-0 w-48 md:w-64 h-48 md:h-64 text-[var(--accent)] opacity-3" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path fill="currentColor" d="M45.3,-72.9C58.5,-67.1,69.1,-54.3,75.5,-40.1C81.9,-25.9,84.1,-10.3,80.1,3.4C76.1,17.1,66,28.8,54.5,39.7C43,50.6,30.2,60.8,16.2,67.2C2.2,73.6,-13,76.2,-25.4,70.1C-37.8,64,-47.4,49.2,-56.5,34.9C-65.6,20.6,-74.2,6.8,-73.4,-6.1C-72.5,-19,-62.3,-30.9,-50.2,-37.8C-38.1,-44.6,-24,-46.4,-10.4,-50.6C3.2,-54.8,16.4,-61.4,30.1,-66.5C43.8,-71.6,58,-75.2,45.3,-72.9Z" transform="translate(100 100)" />
    </svg>
    <svg class="hidden md:block absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-32 md:w-48 h-32 md:h-48 text-[var(--accent)] opacity-2" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path fill="currentColor" d="M39.4,-64.6C51,-58.8,60.5,-47.4,66.7,-34.6C72.9,-21.8,75.8,-7.6,72.1,4.7C68.4,17,58.1,27.4,47.2,37.1C36.3,46.8,24.8,55.8,12.3,60.4C-0.2,65,-13.6,65.2,-25.8,60.1C-38,55,-49,44.6,-57.9,32.2C-66.8,19.8,-73.6,5.3,-72.2,-8.3C-70.8,-21.9,-61.2,-34.6,-49.5,-41.6C-37.8,-48.6,-24,-49.9,-11.4,-47.5C1.2,-45.1,12.9,-38.9,25.7,-32.2C38.5,-25.5,52.4,-18.3,39.4,-64.6Z" transform="translate(100 100)" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-6 border animate-fade-in" style="border-color: var(--border); color: var(--accent); background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 8%, transparent);">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full" style="background-color: var(--accent);"></span>
        Демо-шаблон лендинга
      </div>
      <h1
        class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] mb-6 animate-fade-in animate-fade-in-delay-1 gradient-text"
      >
        Готовый шаблон для вашего лендинга
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto animate-fade-in animate-fade-in-delay-2"
        style="color: var(--text-secondary)"
      >
        Изучите возможности: переключайте темы, смотрите адаптивность, примеры секций — и принимайте решение о заказе сайта.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-fade-in animate-fade-in-delay-3">
        <a
          href="#features"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl text-[var(--text-on-accent)] transition-all duration-200 hover-lift"
          style="background-color: var(--accent);"
        >
          Посмотреть возможности
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl border-2 transition-all duration-200 hover-lift"
          style="color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent);"
        >
          Связаться
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>